# RTAB-Map Database Placeholder
# ================================
# This file is a placeholder for the RTAB-Map SQLite database.
# 
# To create an actual map:
# 1. Connect camera and IMU to Raspberry Pi
# 2. Run: ros2 launch smart_assistive_system mapping_mode.launch.py
# 3. Walk through the environment with the spectacles
# 4. The map will be saved to this location automatically
#
# The actual .db file is a binary SQLite database created by RTAB-Map.
# It contains:
#   - Visual features and keypoints
#   - 3D point clouds
#   - Occupancy grid data
#   - Loop closure constraints
#   - Odometry data
